text: Gurmesh Singh is an Australian politician. He has been a member of the New South Wales Legislative Assembly since 2019, representing Coffs Harbour for the Nationals. Singh was a blueberry and macadamia farmer before his election to parliament. ==References== Category:National Party of Australia members of the Parliament of New South Wales Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Members of the New South Wales Legislative Assembly Category:Australian people of Indian descent Category:Coffs Harbour
